eared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com\">rtCamp</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Nitun Lanjewar\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1734:\"<p>Few years ago we released <a href=\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/wufoo-to-gravity-forms-importer/\">Wufoo to Gravity content importer plugin</a>. We got a good response from users in terms of enhancements to add and also feedback.</p>\n<p>We are organising our list of premium plugins and felt that there were many who wanted to migrate their Wufoo form data to Gravity Forms. It would be better to actually offer this plugin as a free plugin back to the community.</p>\n<p>You can now download use this plugin from the official <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/migrate-wufoo-to-gravity-forms/\">WordPress plugin directory</a>.</p>\n<p>The plugin&#8217;s code can be found on <a href=\"https://github.com/rtCamp/migrate-wufoo-to-gravity-forms\">Github</a>. If you want to report any issues or need to make changes, feel free to send us a pull request.</p>\n<p>If you have already purchased this plugin from our store, you can use our <a href=\"https://rtcamp.com/premium-support/\">premium support</a>  if you need any assistance.</p>\n<p>Your plugin license key is valid for one year as mentioned <a href=\"http://docs.rtcamp.com/license/\">license key</a> will not restrict any feature of the plugin, it was just used to give future updates and premium support.</p>\n<p><strong>Links</strong>: <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/migrate-wufoo-to-gravity-forms/\">Wufoo to Gravity content importer plugin</a> | <a href=\"https://github.com/rtCamp/migrate-wufoo-to-gravity-forms\">Github</a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/migrate-wufoo-form-gravity-form-free/\">Wufoo to Gravity Forms importer WordPress plugin is now Free!</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com\">rtCamp</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/migrate-wufoo-form-gravity-form-free/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"Shmart Payment Gateway Addon for Easy Digital Downloads is Free\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/shmart-addon-easy-digital-downloads-free/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/shmart-addon-easy-digital-downloads-free/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 21 Jan 2016 14:47:17 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:3:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"News\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"https://rtcamp.com/?p=140643\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:443:\"<p>The Shmart Payment Gateway Addon for Easy Digital Downloads allows using Shmart payment gateway with your EasyDigitalDownload store and is now part of the official WordPress plugin repo.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/shmart-addon-easy-digital-downloads-free/\">Shmart Payment Gateway Addon for Easy Digital Downloads is Free</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com\">rtCamp</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Aditya Kane\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1647:\"<p>Few months ago we introduced <a href=\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/shmart-payment-gateway-easy-digital-downloads-plugin/\">Shmart Payment Gateway addon</a> for Easy Digital Downloads plugin. This plugin add-on was mainly developed by us for our <a href=\"https://rtcamp.com/products/\">store</a> that runs on Easy Digital Downloads. We are streamlining our product line and decided to make some of our premium plugins available free.</p>\n<h2>What is Shmart?</h2>\n<p>It is a payment gateway that is very popular in India.  <a href=\"http://shmart.in/\">Shmart Payment Gateway</a> allows users to purchase the product in Indian currency (INR). It also accepts payments via all VISA and MasterCard debit and credit cards and internet banking of 27 major banks and IMPS payment option with over 55 banks.</p>\n<p>This add-on that allows using Shmart payment gateway with your EasyDigitalDownload store is now part of the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/payment-gateway-easy-digital-downloads-shmart/\">official WordPress plugin repo</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Links: </strong><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/payment-gateway-easy-digital-downloads-shmart/\">Shmart Payment Gateway for EDD Addon</a> | <a href=\"https://github.com/rtCamp/payment-gateway-easydigitaldownloads-shmart\">Github</a> | <a href=\"https://github.com/rtCamp/payment-gateway-easydigitaldownloads-shmart/wiki\">Documentation</a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/shmart-addon-easy-digital-downloads-free/\">Shmart Payment Gateway Addon for Easy Digital Downloads is Free</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com\">rtCamp</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"https://rtcamp.com/blog/shmart-addon-easy-digital-downloads-free/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\"